data.description: Beautifully upgraded Cachet-built luxury home in the desirable gated community of Serenade in Vistancia! Enter this amazing home through the elegant glass-paned front door & upgraded luxury vinyl plank flooring. The spacious den is a great place to get some work done & allows for privacy w/ the double glass french doors. The home is set up for entertaining w/ adjoining formal dining room, family room & kitchen. Relax in the family room & enjoy the surround sound & built-in gas fireplace on the stone-accented media wall. The recently remodeled kitchen boasts granite countertops, a high-top bar, large granite-top island w/ sink, double ovens, 5-burner gas cooktop, new undermount sinks & faucets & butler's pantry. The owner's suite is conveniently located on the first floor. Enter through the bonus room that can flex as a workout room or a study. Remodeled primary en-suite has a large walk-in shower w/ upgraded showerhead, bluetooth lighting, a soaking tub, high sinks, spacious walk-in closet & a separate vanity. Well thought-out floor plan also includes 2 more bedrooms & 2 more full bathrooms on the main floor (one of them is an en-suite). 4th & 5th bedrooms and 4th bathroom are upstairs w/ a large adjoining loft. Enjoy some outdoor time in either the private front courtyard or resort-style backyard w/ a refreshing pool & a water feature & newly placed sod. Entertain under the pergola w/ the built-in BBQ island, fridge & table top fire pit for those chilly winter nights. Lots of privacy in the back with no rear neighbors. The 2 separate garages offer plenty of parking for 3 cars along with upper storage & built-in cabinets. Lots of pride of ownership in this home. ACs are newer as of 2016, 2020, and 2022. Pool has a new variable speed pump, equipment piping & filter vessel. Entire irrigation system for front & back yards was replaced in 2022. Enjoy the delicious fruit off of the grapefruit, lemon & orange trees! Vistancia is a 7100-acre master-planned award-winning community, with nationally-recognized home builders, two golf courses, multiple parks, swimming pools & community centers, 3.5 miles of Discovery Trail, luxury resident amenities, top-rated schools, and convenient access to retail & restaurants, all surrounded by the incredible beauty of the Sonoran Desert. The future FIVE NORTH at VISTANCIA, a 320-acre commercial core, envisioned to be a dynamic & vibrant lifestyle destination, will be just down the street. Vistancia has ranked as the #1 Master Planned Community in AZ for 10 years in a row (2014-2023)! Come & see why!
